<plot>What do a stripper, a pissed-off night manager, a death-obsessed grad student, and a ditched housewife have in common? They cry for strangers at funerals... and get paid for it. A dark comedy about a motley group of part-time professional funeral mourners who are paid to cry for complete strangers by a dubious funeral director. However, when a familiar face is suffering, they fail miserably at what they should do best.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?223047</url></doc>
